text: Jean Scott (born 14 March 1994) is a Costa Rican footballer who plays for Sporting San José in the Costa Rican second division. Scott made his debut for the senior Costa Rica national football team at the Avaya Stadium on the 2 February 2019 against the United States. ==References== Category:Guadalupe F.C. players Category:Costa Rica international footballers Category:Costa Rican footballers Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Association footballers not categorized by position
